      "id": "69f437baba6993831050b52d",
      "text": "剣禅一致",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612732,
      "updated": 1777612732
    },
    {
      "id": "69f437bc000000000041fad5",
      "text": ">沢庵和尚が「不動智神妙録」で説いた剣の境地。剣道の究極の境地は禅の無念無想の境地と同一であるという意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612732,
      "updated": 1777612771
    },
    {
      "id": "69f437d7000000000041fad6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612759,
      "updated": 1777612759
    },
    {
      "id": "69f43816000000000041fada",
      "text": "[沢庵宗彭]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612822,
      "updated": 1777612863
    },
    {
      "id": "69f437e6000000000041fad7",
      "text": "[柳生宗矩]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612774,
      "updated": 1777612820
    },
    {
      "id": "69f43814000000000041fad8",
      "text": "[無念無想]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777612820,
      "updated": 1777612820
    },
